    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start with the cultural intelligence part. but we're looking for specific, concrete standards. like, when our clients are attending high-level galas or international business dinners, what are the standard rules for things like dress codes, table manners, and even how they should carry themselves? what should the \"gold standard\" look like?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
