    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so i'm seeing a lot of western-style suits and black tie in these \"gold standards.\" but what if we're talking about a high-level event in somewhere like Lagos, or Mumbai, or Kyoto? like, if we want to be considered truly sophisticated in those regions, do they follow these same rules, or do they have their own versions of what's professional and high-class?",
